EXPLAINING OUR DOCKERFILE 

Smaller image
node:18-alpine

👉 Much lighter → faster pull → faster deploy on EKS

✅ 2. Faster builds (very important)
COPY package*.json ./
RUN npm ci --only=production
COPY . .

👉 Docker caches dependencies
👉 No reinstall unless package.json changes

✅ 3. Production install
npm install --production

👉 Skips dev dependencies → smaller + safer

